<D>__{oh that's not necessary.}
<A>__{but they give up their seats anyway. hazel and gus take them. we see various passengers watching. hazel ignores the attention until a little girl (6, cute braids) appears.}
<C>__{little girl}
<D>__{what's in your nose?}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{it's called a cannula. these tubes give me oxygen and help me breathe.}
